1
00:00:14,725 --> 00:00:18,487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

2
00:00:18,562 --> 00:00:22,162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

3
00:00:22,287 --> 00:00:25,437
♪Your “same here” carries
a touch of resolve♪

4
00:00:25,862 --> 00:00:29,412
♪Pack my bags,
we can set off right now♪

5
00:00:29,637 --> 00:00:33,112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

6
00:00:33,250 --> 00:00:36,712
♪The journey itself is what truly matters
before the destination♪

7
00:00:36,787 --> 00:00:40,975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

8
00:00:41,025 --> 00:00:42,612
♪Connect♪

9
00:00:42,625 --> 00:00:43,275
♪Let's go!♪

10
00:00:43,612 --> 00:00:47,137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

11
00:00:47,237 --> 00:00:50,675
♪Today, no dwelling on
negative emotions♪

12
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:53,450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

13
00:00:53,450 --> 00:00:55,262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

14
00:00:55,262 --> 00:00:58,199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

15
00:00:59,075 --> 00:01:02,375
=Love in A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

16
00:01:02,675 --> 00:01:06,275
=Episode 24=

17
00:01:17,160 --> 00:01:17,960
Ze?

18
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:20,040
Zhu.

19
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:23,080
What's the occasion today?

20
00:01:23,320 --> 00:01:24,480
You're dressed so formally.

21
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:26,920
I asked my dad

22
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:28,840
to contact a hospital in Singapore.

23
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:32,960
They can arrange consultations with
some of the world's top specialists.

24
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:35,480
You can receive treatment there

25
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:36,560
while attending university.

26
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:39,240
Will you go with me?

27
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:43,560
I mean,

28
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:46,640
I've actually liked you for a long time,

29
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:47,240
Zhu.

30
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:49,440
from the very first time you met me,

31
00:01:49,960 --> 00:01:51,880
you were wearing a floral dress,

32
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:54,290
kind of like the one
you're wearing today.

33
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:57,080
Your hair was soft and loose
over your shoulders.

34
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:58,240
You called me Ze.

35
00:01:59,080 --> 00:02:00,080
At the moment, I knew

36
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:01,120
I already liked you

37
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:02,240
and fallen for you.

38
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:07,230
Every second and every day
when I wasn't in Hai City,

39
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:09,100
all I could think about
was coming back here.

40
00:02:09,200 --> 00:02:10,760
And every day after I came back,

41
00:02:11,100 --> 00:02:13,190
all I could think about
was whether I'd run into you.

42
00:02:13,760 --> 00:02:16,040
All the people I've met

43
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:17,480
and all the things I've experienced,

44
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:20,880
those fleeting moments of happiness

45
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:22,520
don't compare to your smile.

46
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:25,200
If you smile at me once,

47
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:26,960
I can stay happy
for a very, very long time.

48
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:29,720
Zhu,

49
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:32,480
do you think I'm beyond saving?

50
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,880
I understand everything you mean.

51
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,480
And you know how I feel.

52
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:45,640
But I can't go with you.

53
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:49,080
I know. I know.

54
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:52,920
I just felt that I should properly

55
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:55,400
and sincerely tell you

56
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:57,700
about the love I've kept hidden
in my heart for so long.

57
00:02:59,040 --> 00:03:02,760
Now I have no regrets.

58
00:03:03,175 --> 00:03:04,362
Don't worry.

59
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:06,325
I'll focus on my treatment.

60
00:03:08,050 --> 00:03:09,170
When you come back,

61
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,800
we'll go fly kites together.

62
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,600
Then,

63
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:15,720
when I return,

64
00:03:16,300 --> 00:03:17,990
you'll be the first person
I come to see.

65
00:03:32,500 --> 00:03:34,190
Make sure you take care
of your treatment.

66
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,280
I'll go now.

67
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:56,080
Lu, I'll be waiting for you.

68
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,880
Yes, girl.

69
00:03:59,360 --> 00:03:59,937
Don't worry.

70
00:04:02,500 --> 00:04:03,400
The surgery is about to start.

71
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,700
The family members should wait outside.

72
00:04:18,962 --> 00:04:21,637
(In operation)

73
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,160
Family of Lu Zhu?

74
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,600
Here.

75
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,200
I'm her father.

76
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:32,480
The patient has lost too much blood
during surgery.

77
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:34,160
Her vital signs aren't very stable
right now.

78
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,900
We hope you'll prepare
yourselves mentally.

79
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:38,480
What do you mean?

80
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,080
Isn't this

81
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:40,400
just a simple

82
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:41,800
splenectomy?

83
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,240
She has Gaucher disease.

84
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:44,840
This illness can change

85
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:46,040
unpredictably.

86
00:04:46,100 --> 00:04:47,760
I'm only informing you of the situation.

87
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:49,560
But don't worry.

88
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,040
We'll do everything we can.

89
00:04:53,320 --> 00:04:54,440
Doctor.

90
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:55,360
I have money.

91
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,280
Doctor, I...

92
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:57,400
Mr. Lu.

93
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,640
Don't worry.

94
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,280
Lu will make it through.

95
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:11,440
Man,

96
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,720
have I committed too many sins?

97
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,480
Is Heaven punishing me?

98
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:20,240
My family is being punished.

99
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,800
They're leaving me one by one.

100
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:29,040
And I don't even get a chance
to make things right.

101
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,520
Mr. Lu.

102
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:35,200
Mr. Lu...

103
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,040
Please don't be like this.

104
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:46,600
Lu will make it through.

105
00:06:19,312 --> 00:06:19,950
How is it?

106
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,880
Does it look good?

107
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,960
Why did you draw your head so big?

108
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,480
What do you mean by big?

109
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:30,320
You have no sense of appreciation.

110
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:17,960
Zhu.

111
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,480
Stop filming me.

112
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:41,640
Stop it.

113
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:43,400
Sometimes,

114
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,560
things aren't simply black or white.

115
00:07:47,020 --> 00:07:48,990
The gray area in between
is often the best answer.

116
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:50,080
You're too intense.

117
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:51,000
Like a wild horse.

118
00:07:53,660 --> 00:07:54,560
None of your business.

119
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,960
If I don't care, who will?

120
00:08:02,487 --> 00:08:05,202
I said I don't need a brother.

121
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,440
Then what do you need?

122
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,840
(Tomb of the Loving Mother, Shen Qi)

123
00:08:34,878 --> 00:08:37,103
(Tomb of Beloved Daughter, Lu Zhu)

124
00:08:37,103 --> 00:08:43,053
(Tomb of Beloved Daughter, Lu Sun)

125
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:48,980
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

126
00:09:49,205 --> 00:09:52,993
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

127
00:09:53,168 --> 00:09:57,243
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

128
00:09:57,243 --> 00:10:01,380
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

129
00:10:01,505 --> 00:10:05,280
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

130
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:09,055
♪I'll learn to stop longing for
what's gone♪

131
00:10:09,055 --> 00:10:11,330
♪The you in my memories♪

132
00:10:11,330 --> 00:10:13,343
♪Will fade from clarity♪

133
00:10:13,343 --> 00:10:18,780
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

134
00:10:20,343 --> 00:10:25,780
♪Forget you completely?♪

135
00:10:43,158 --> 00:10:47,658
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

136
00:10:47,883 --> 00:10:51,671
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

137
00:10:51,846 --> 00:10:55,921
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

138
00:10:55,921 --> 00:11:00,058
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

139
00:11:00,183 --> 00:11:03,958
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

140
00:11:03,958 --> 00:11:07,733
♪I'll learn to stop longing for
what's gone♪

141
00:11:07,733 --> 00:11:10,008
♪The you in my memories♪

142
00:11:10,008 --> 00:11:12,021
♪Will fade from clarity♪

143
00:11:12,021 --> 00:11:17,458
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

144
00:11:19,021 --> 00:11:24,458
♪Forget you completely?♪
